Title: D-Branes in Linear Dilaton Backgrounds

Authors: Arvind Rajaraman and Moshe Rozali

Comments: 14 pages, Latex. Typos corrected and references added

Journal-ref: JHEP 9912 (1999) 005

We construct a Dirichlet boundary state for linear dilaton backgrounds. Thestate is conformally invariant and satisfies Cardy's conditions. We apply thisconstruction to two dimensional string theory.